  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-4 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
    <SectionHeading title="Writing Philosophy" />
    <p class="text-gray-300">
      I believe in creating stories that not only entertain but also challenge
      readers to think differently about the world around them. Each book is a
      journey we take together, exploring the depths of human experience through
      the power of words.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-4 border border-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
    <SectionHeading title="Connect" />
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 text-lg">
      I love hearing from readers, fellow writers, and creative collaborators! The best way to connect is through my social channels below—whether you want to share your thoughts, ask a question, or explore a partnership, just reach out. I check my DMs and mentions regularly.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-2">
      <span class="mb-3 text-blue-200 text-base">For the latest updates, events, and direct interaction, join the conversation on Facebook:</span>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100091741922032" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-lg font-semibold text-lg transition mt-2 mb-2">
        <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M22.675 0h-21.35C.596 0 0 .592 0 1.326v21.348C0 23.408.596 24 1.325 24H12.82v-9.294H9.692V11.01h3.127V8.413c0-3.1 1.893-4.788 4.659-4.788 1.325 0 2.463.099 2.797.143v3.24l-1.92.001c-1.504 0-1.797.715-1.797 1.763v2.313h3.587l-.467 3.696h-3.12V24h6.116C23.404 24 24 23.408 24 22.674V1.326C24 .592 23.404 0 22.675 0"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Chris Berry - Author on Facebook</span>
      </a>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-center mt-3 max-w-md">
        Follow my Facebook Page for the latest news, release announcements, behind-the-scenes content, and to connect directly via comments and Messenger. I’d love to hear from you!
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center mt-2">
      For media or business inquiries, please DM me on LinkedIn or Instagram.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
